{"tid":1957343,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"汪 明 荃 女 士 慘 遭 吳 業 坤 「調 戲」：可 唔 可 以 噴 我 ？","createTime":"2020-04-03T22:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T06:56:03.000Z","uid":24160,"like":44,"dislike":158,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"1e224b5d5fb080cda0c7abfeb9266c0f7b1fe0b4","tid":1957343,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T22:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200403/s00009/6f10ce969c3b8e255da3ea80376b4ab5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200403%2Fs00009%2F6f10ce969c3b8e255da3ea80376b4ab5.jpg&h=ec98a302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情肆虐，「阿姐」汪明荃早前捐出口罩、搓手液及消毒濕紙巾予醫護人員，阿姐還拍片呼籲隔離人士，要遵守強制家居檢疫令，讓市民同心打勝疫戰。昨天阿姐在ig貼相，指收到由林小明先生送給她的新防疫用品「納米滅菌噴霧」，阿姐留言多謝林小明，並祝福對方家人健康﹑平安和開心。而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吳業坤亦在阿姐該貼文留言：「可唔可以噴我？」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>豈有此理 連阿姐都敢挑逗！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/r7089PA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fr7089PA.gif&h=0efeeb57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>坤哥要噴就噴呢支啦！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/http://photouploads.com/images/c13840.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200403/1585888581034/汪明荃獲贈「納米滅菌噴霧」-吳業坤-可唔可以噴我\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200403%2F1585888581034%2F%E6%B1%AA%E6%98%8E%E8%8D%83%E7%8D%B2%E8%B4%88%E3%80%8C%E7%B4%8D%E7%B1%B3%E6%BB%85%E8%8F%8C%E5%99%B4%E9%9C%A7%E3%80%8D-%E5%90%B3%E6%A5%AD%E5%9D%A4-%E5%8F%AF%E5%94%